    <p> The food was good even without side dishes. Afterward, we quickly made our way to the nearby promenade and enjoyed our last sunset together for a long, long time. </p>
    <p> When it started to get dark, I drove her to the airport, and we savored the final moments before the international security area opened for her flight and I could no longer accompany her. </p>
    <p> Then I drove back to the campsite and suddenly found myself alone. Which I find pretty depressing. Tomorrow I'll start my journey back to Sydney, where I'll work again for a few months at ProductReview.com.au. </p>
    <p> Now I'm off to my big and lonely bed. Good night!!! </p>

